    "The relative 70B judge outperforms even SFT and is the best method on Nectar dataset.",
    "Comparison to JudgeLM: Unlike the 70B judge, JudgeLM is not clearly better than our original base judges.",
    "In rating prediction tasks (Table 1), we improve over JudgeLM in MSE (LS judge), MAE (LS judge on Summarize from Feedback), and accuracy (MN judge).",
    "The correlation metrics of our judges are superior to those of JudgeLM.",
    "On Offset Bias dataset (Table 2), BTL2 significantly improves over both absolute and relative JudgeLM in all metrics."
